(text_box "Fit ONE PTT driver (A, B or C). Passive front-end R1..R10 / C1..C5 / RV1 / RV2 / D1 / D2 is identical in both the minimal and the UV-5R build; only the radio-side endpoints change. R1,R2 + C2,C3 = 2-pole reconstruction LPF fc~4.8kHz (kills 38.4kHz DAC images). C1 = DC block. R3/RV1 = pad + level trim. RV2 = RX level (omit for a DATA OUT port). C4 = DC block/HPF. R5,R6 = mid-rail bias 1.65V. R7/C5 = SAR sampling snubber (NOT an audio filter -- never fit 100nF). D1,D2 (BAT54S or 2x1N4148) clamp GPIO33 to the rails. R8 = 470R opto LED current. R10 = gate/base pull that keeps PTT unkeyed through reset." (at 160 150 0) (size 240 70) (stroke (width 0.127) (type solid)) (fill (type none)) (effects (font (size 1.4 1.4)) (justify left top)) (uuid f446ccf1-981f-44db-b3fc-aa0dd74ec56d))
  (sheet_instances
    (path "/" (page "1")))
  (embedded_fonts no)
)
